                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   Business Briefs
                              
	 Mumbai, Sept. 15: BSNL and the UKs Cable amp; Wireless have signed an MoU for sharing of networks and other telecom infrastructure. Cable amp; Wireless will support BSNLs global network expansion.                            
	 New Delhi, Sept. 15: The government has appointed Ashok Chawla as the secretary of the department of economic affairs. M. Madhavan Nambiar was appointed as the secretary of the ministry of civil aviation, in place of Chawla.                                                                                                                         
